initiateScan

public static AlertDialog initiateScan(Activity activity)
function name : initiateScan This function is called from the activity class to start the process of scanning the barcode. current activity has to be passed as the parameter in the function. The function will result in display of the dialog box for downloading the barcode scanner application if it is not already installed, else it will start the process of scanning.
